'''''Droids'' 3''' is the third issue of the [[Star Wars: Droids (1986)|''Star Wars: Droids'']] series of comics. The story is split into two chapters, "The Scarlet Pirate Part 1" and "The Scarlet Pirate Part 2: End of the Game." The issue was published on [[May 13]], [[1986]] by [[Marvel Comics]].<ref name="Droids 3 date" />

==Plot summary==
[[C-3PO/Legends|C-3PO]] and [[R2-D2/Legends|R2-D2]] are purchased by [[Ambassador/Legends|Ambassador]] [[Zell]], who wants the [[Droid/Legends|droids]] to look after his son, [[Llez]], while he's away on business. But the boy feels neglected, and runs away and joins the space [[Pirate/Legends|pirate]] [[Reddjak]] and his crew, who are using the boy to get to Zell.

